summary:
▪ Defence and security policy specialist, currently re-training to enter into the world of cyber security. Check in on me again in a few months' time!
▪ Four years working for Ministry of Foreign Affairs & two+ years for Ministry of Defence. Focus countries: the Netherlands, Norway, Russian Federation . 
▪ Linguist. Fluency in English, Norwegian and Dutch. Working knowledge of Danish. High level of proficiency in Russian (B2 certified). 
▪ IT Experience: 4+ years as first-line IT support officer & LAN technician.
▪ Certified First Aid Provider (EHBO)  - including CPR, catastrophic bleeding, children's first aid & non-life threatening conditions.
